To run this code, you need to install pyprocessing 
# easy_install pyprocessing

Prior to above command, you may also need to install pyglet manually
http://www.pyglet.org/download.html
# wget http://pyglet.googlecode.com/files/pyglet-1.1.4.tar.gz
# tar xvzf pyglet-1.1.4.tar.gz
# cd pyglet-1.1.4
# python setup install

For all the code to run smotthly, you may also need to install OpenGL forpython
# easy_install pyopengl


